684    /**
685     * builds CustomLineItemDraft without checking for non-null required values
686     * @return CustomLineItemDraft
687     */
688    public CustomLineItemDraft buildUnchecked() {
689        return new CustomLineItemDraftImpl(name, money, taxedPrice, totalPrice, slug, quantity, state, taxCategory,
690            taxRate, externalTaxRate, discountedPricePerQuantity, shippingDetails);
691    }
692
693    /**
694     * factory method for an instance of CustomLineItemDraftBuilder
695     * @return builder
696     */
697    public static CustomLineItemDraftBuilder of() {
698        return new CustomLineItemDraftBuilder();
699    }
700
701    /**
702     * create builder for CustomLineItemDraft instance
703     * @param template instance with prefilled values for the builder
704     * @return builder
705     */
706    public static CustomLineItemDraftBuilder of(final CustomLineItemDraft template) {
707        CustomLineItemDraftBuilder builder = new CustomLineItemDraftBuilder();
708        builder.name = template.getName();
709        builder.money = template.getMoney();
710        builder.taxedPrice = template.getTaxedPrice();
711        builder.totalPrice = template.getTotalPrice();
712        builder.slug = template.getSlug();
713        builder.quantity = template.getQuantity();
714        builder.state = template.getState();
715        builder.taxCategory = template.getTaxCategory();
716        builder.taxRate = template.getTaxRate();
717        builder.externalTaxRate = template.getExternalTaxRate();
718        builder.discountedPricePerQuantity = template.getDiscountedPricePerQuantity();
719        builder.shippingDetails = template.getShippingDetails();
720        return builder;
721    }
